{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a001", "atom_type": "HEADING", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 1, "line_end": 1, "verbatim": "# FA — Examples", "parent_section": "§FA [FA — Examples]", "heading_level": 1, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a002", "atom_type": "HEADING", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 3, "line_end": 3, "verbatim": "## Example 1", "parent_section": "§FA [FA — Examples]", "heading_level": 2, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a003", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 5, "line_end": 5, "verbatim": "The following example CRF collects severity and symptoms data at multiple time points about a migraine event, relative to dosing.", "parent_section": "§FA.1 [Example 1]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a004", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 7, "line_end": 7, "verbatim": "In this example trial, migraines and symptoms associated with migraines were considered clinical events rather than reportable adverse events. The migraine, its sponsor identifier (i.e., the \"Migraine Reference Number\" on the CRF), and its start date were represented in a CE record.", "parent_section": "§FA.1 [Example 1]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a005", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 9, "line_end": 9, "verbatim": "**ce.xpt**", "parent_section": "§FA.1 [Example 1]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
