{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a083", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 129, "line_end": 129, "verbatim": "In this example, the occurrence of prespecified adverse events was solicited at every visit and the visit date was used as the date of collection. The data collected meet criterion 3 in Section 6.4.1, When to Use Findings About Events or Interventions; that is, data that indicate the occurrence of prespecified AEs.", "parent_section": "§FA.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["Section 6.4.1"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a084", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 131, "line_end": 131, "verbatim": "**Rows 1, 4:** \"Headache\" was reported at both visits.", "parent_section": "§FA.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a085", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 132, "line_end": 132, "verbatim": "**Rows 2, 5:** \"Respiratory infection\" was not present at either visit.", "parent_section": "§FA.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a086", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 133, "line_end": 133, "verbatim": "**Row 3:** The investigator did not ask the subject about the occurrence of nausea. This was represented by FASTAT=\"NOT DONE\".", "parent_section": "§FA.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
