{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a096", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 147, "line_end": 147, "verbatim": "For each prespecified adverse event for which FAORRES = \"Y\", the adverse event has a record in the AE domain with AEPRESP = \"Y\". No relationship was collected to link the FAAE record for the occurrence indicator test with the AE entries, so no RELREC was created.", "parent_section": "§FA.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a097", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 149, "line_end": 149, "verbatim": "Note that not all AE expected variables are included in the following example.", "parent_section": "§FA.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
