{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a102", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 158, "line_end": 158, "verbatim": "**Row 1:** Comparison of this AE record with the FA dataset records for \"Headache\" shows that there are 2 records with FAOBJ=\"Headache\". FAORRES=\"Y\" indicates that this AE record is associated with both FA records, because this headache started before visit 2 and ended between visits 2 and 3.", "parent_section": "§FA.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a103", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 160, "line_end": 160, "verbatim": "**Row 2:** Comparison of this AE record with the FA dataset shows that this AE started and ended in the time between visits 2 and 3, and is consistent with the FA response for FAOBJ=\"Nausea\" for visit 3.", "parent_section": "§FA.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a104", "atom_type": "HEADING", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 162, "line_end": 162, "verbatim": "## Example 5", "parent_section": "§FA [FA — Examples]", "heading_level": 2, "sibling_index": 5, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a105", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 164, "line_end": 164, "verbatim": "In this example, data about prespecified symptoms of the disease under study were collected on a daily basis. Although the date of the assessment was captured in the CRF header (not shown), start and end timing of the prespecified symptoms was not.", "parent_section": "§FA.5 [Example 5]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a106", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 166, "line_end": 166, "verbatim": "The collected data were represented in FA because they meet criterion 1 in Section 6.4.1, When to Use Findings About Events or Interventions, that is, data that do not describe an event or intervention as a whole. In addition, the volume of vomit data met criterion 2 data (\"about\" an event or intervention), having qualifiers that can be represented in Findings variables (e.g., units, method).", "parent_section": "§FA.5 [Example 5]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["Section 6.4.1"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a107", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 168, "line_end": 168, "verbatim": "This SDTM example represents data from 2 visits for 1 subject. FAEVINTX indicates that assessments were for the previous 24 hours.", "parent_section": "§FA.5 [Example 5]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a108", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 170, "line_end": 170, "verbatim": "**Rows 1-4:** Show the results for the vomiting tests at visit 1. Because the number of episodes was recorded as \">10\", this is represented in FASTRESC but not in FASTRESN.", "parent_section": "§FA.5 [Example 5]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a109", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 171, "line_end": 171, "verbatim": "**Rows 5-7:** Show the results for the diarrhea tests at visit 1.", "parent_section": "§FA.5 [Example 5]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
