{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a136", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 205, "line_end": 205, "verbatim": "*Note: The FA Example 6 CRF shows severity assessed at Visits 2-6 for up to 3 concurrent AEs per subject. The data collected about severity at each visit represents snapshots or slices of the AE over time, meeting criterion 1 for When to Use Findings About Events or Interventions.*", "parent_section": "§FA.6 [Example 6]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a137", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 207, "line_end": 207, "verbatim": "AE collection started after visit 1, so the first severity data was collected at visit 2.", "parent_section": "§FA.6 [Example 6]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a138", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 209, "line_end": 209, "verbatim": "The collected data met criterion 1 in Section 6.4.1, When to Use Findings About Events or Interventions, for data that do not describe an event or intervention as a whole.", "parent_section": "§FA.6 [Example 6]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["Section 6.4.1"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmFA_ex_a139", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FA/examples.md", "line_start": 211, "line_end": 211, "verbatim": "In this example, the sponsor populated AESEV with the maximum severity over the course of the event. This was not directly collected, but rather determined from the weekly maximum severity assessments collected on the CRF. For clarity, only selected variables in the AE dataset are shown here.", "parent_section": "§FA.6 [Example 6]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T08:00:00Z"}}
